Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.input

Class InputServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<InputComponentType,Input>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.input.InputServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
InputService, TableFilter, TableInsertion, Insertion
public class InputServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<InputComponentType,Input> implements InputService
Provides service-level operations for interacting with input components.

This class manages interactions with input fields, such as inserting values, clearing fields, retrieving values, checking states, and handling table-based operations. The actual interactions are delegated to specific Input implementations based on the provided InputComponentType.
